The Proposal: -
The Vimukt Jati nomadic tribe category in the state of Maharashtra has many castes, tribes and still exists.
They are living a migratory life by travelling. Laman, Banjara, Vanjari, Dhangar, Pardhi etc.
There are many groups of Tands / hamlets in which people belonging to these castes / tribes have lived for many years.
However, such hamlets or hamlets do not have basic facilities and tend to modernize.
However, the majority of the community in this category lives in poverty. At present, in the Tande, Wadi, or Basti
This category of society should lead a stable life in the same place where it resides.
